{"lang": "ja_JP", "eventid": "act45side", "eventName": "安らかな譫言", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "SS-4", "avgTag": "戦闘前", "storyName": "客間の迷宮", "storyInfo": "初華の夢の中で、祥子はひと気のない小さな島に到着する。その島で、初華は孤独に祥子の帰りを待ち続けていた。初華は友人になったエイヤフィヤトラからの問いかけをきっかけに、祥子に対する自身の感情と向き合うことになる。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g10_dreamcastlestage", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>繊細で柔らかい記憶を包み込む。誰の目にも触れないように。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>でも声が枯れるほどの想いを、どうあの人に届ければいいの？</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>我、悲しみを恐れるなかれ。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g3_islandharbor", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_harbor_busy", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shipwhistle", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.5}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_footstep_stonestep", "volume": 0.6, "channel": "step", "loop": "false"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "step", "fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstpwalk", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "o"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "o", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#1$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "揺れる甲板から堅牢な大地に足を踏み出すと、祥子はようやく安心感を覚えた。"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嬢ちゃん、話に付き合ってくれてありがとな。", "name": "親切な船長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "この島は随分離れてるからな。あんたがいなきゃ、一人でだだっ広い海を眺めて運転するところだった。想像するだけで、退屈すぎて気がおかしくなりそうだ。", "name": "親切な船長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "こちらこそ、海の上の興味深いお話をたくさん聞かせていただきありがとうございました。", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#1$2"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "その恰好からして地元の子じゃなさそうだな。なんでこんな誰も来ないような小さい島に来たんだ？", "name": "親切な船長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……捜している人がいますの。", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "この島の人か？", "name": "親切な船長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……おそらく、違います。", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そりゃ珍しいな。この島から出ていく奴はいても、自分から来る奴なんて初めて聞いたぞ。", "name": "親切な船長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "わたくしも、確信があって来たわけではなく……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夢に入った時、祥子の手元にあったのはこの島への乗船券だけだった。モーフィアスの悪戯かもしれないという考えが頭によぎったが他に取れる選択肢もなかった。"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_slapcloth_light", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（肩を叩く）まぁ、心配すんな！　この島に住んでる奴は少ないから、住民に訊いたらすぐに見つかるだろう！", "name": "親切な船長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……ええ。", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#1$2"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "けど嬢ちゃん、その子が見つかっても見つからなくても、昼過ぎには戻ってくるんだぞ。", "name": "親切な船長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "この島は船の便が少ないからな。もし逃しちまったら、次に帰れるのは早くても来月になっちまう。", "name": "親切な船長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ですが、それではもう時間が……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "うーん、そう言われてもな……", "name": "親切な船長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少しだけなら待てるが、夜の航海は危険だからな。日が暮れる前には帰らないといけないんだよ。", "name": "親切な船長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……わかりました。急ぎます！", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.3, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$beach", "channel": "bc", "loop": "true", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（歌声）アーアーアー……♪", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "はい、聞こえます。", "name": "？？"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_fssand", "channel": "ystep", "loop": "true", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "ystep", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小さな歌声）アーアーアー……♪", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "？？"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_runstop", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "離れて何度か歌ってみたけど……ダメだった？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……はい。何も聞こえませんでした。", "name": "？？"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……とりあえずアイマスク外すね。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bc", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "bg_beach_1/bg_beach_2", "solidwidth": "920/920", "solidheight": 720.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_dim_openeye", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "どうでしたか？", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ちょっと言いにくいんだけど……前やった時と比べて、また聞こえる範囲が狭くなってるみたい。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そうですか……分かりました。これからフィールドワークに出る時は、もっと周りの状況に気を配るようにしますね。", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#2$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#11$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "エイヤフィヤトラちゃん、やっぱり危ないんじゃないかな……", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#11$2"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "島に来てどれくらい経つの？", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#11$2"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二ヶ月くらいです。", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#11$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聴力が落ちてるのに、ちゃんと診てくれるお医者さんもいなければ治療方法もないんだよ。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#11$2"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今日は港に船が来てるはず。荷物をまとめるのを手伝ってあげるから、すぐにでも帰ろう？", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#11$2"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そういうわけにはいきません。まだこの島の火山のデータを集め終わっていないので……", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "でも、エイヤフィヤトラちゃんの身体は――", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "この島に来る前に、ロドスの先生に診てもらったんです。", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "その……確かにあまり良い状態とは言えないんですが、先生と約束したんです。三ヶ月だけって。", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "火山の研究が私にとってすごく大切だってことは先生も分かってくれてますから、最後には納得してくれました。", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#13$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初華さん、私は火山が好きなんです。あなたが星を見るのが好きなように。", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#13$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "私たちが初めて出会ったのも、私が山で迷子になっていた夜でしたね。あの時、ちょうどあなたは星空を見上げていました。", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#13$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#13$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……これから山にフィールドワークに行く時は、私も絶対一緒に行くからね。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#13$2"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "はい、ありがとうございます！", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#12$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$beach", "channel": "bc1", "loop": "true", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bc1", "fadetime": 3.5}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今日は天気がいいなぁ……", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "私、初華さんの歌が聴きたいです。", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "こんな良いお天気の日は、歌を聴きながら遠くの火山や海を眺めるのにぴったりですから。", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#13$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "いいよ。じゃあちょっと近寄るね……", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#13$2"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-120,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初華が距離を少し詰めると、エイヤフィヤトラは小さな耳をぴんとそばだてた。その耳には、ちらりと補聴器が覗いている。"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#3$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（深く息を吸う）", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#3$2"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "「ねじれた空を　描いて思うの」", "x": 300.0, "y": 200.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n「羽根のない君　堕ちればいい」", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n「触れてしまった神聖なもの」", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n「今夜　私の神話になって――」", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n「……」", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clapsologirl"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "とっても素敵でした！", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#13$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#13$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……ありがとう。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#13$2"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初めて聴きましたが、どなたが作った歌なんでしょう？　もしかしてこの島の歌ですか？", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "私も分からないんだ。前にどこかで聴いたのかな、知らないうちに歌えるようになってて……", "name": "三角初華"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "でも、初華さん……なんだかすごく寂しそうです。", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#3$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#8$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#8$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "え……？", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#8$2"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "41_g5_siestaunbuiltland_d", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_021", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "なに？　三角初華？", "name": "疑い深い島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_021"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ジョン、聞いたことあるか？", "name": "疑い深い島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_021"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "いいや。名前からして島の外の人間だろ？", "name": "同じく疑い深い島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "なにか手がかりだけでも頂けませんか？", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "島で一番顔が広いあなたならきっと何か知っていると、先ほど近くにいたおばあ様からお聞きしましたの。", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_021", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "うーん……なんせ人が少ない島だからな。誰も聞いたことがないってことは、最近来た人なんじゃないか？", "name": "疑い深い島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_021"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そういえば、確か火山の裏手に別荘があって、そこに変わった奴が住んでるって噂があったな。", "name": "疑い深い島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_021"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ああ……俺も聞いたことがあるぞ。", "name": "同じく疑い深い島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "名前は忘れちまったが、そいつなんじゃないか？", "name": "同じく疑い深い島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "その別荘はどちらですの！？", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_021", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ほら、この海岸道路沿いを北に二十キロ、回り込むように山の裏側まで行けば、あの別荘が見つかるはずだ。", "name": "疑念を捨てた島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_021"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ありがとうございます。二十キロなら、車で行けば三十分ほど……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_021", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嬢ちゃん、ここに車はないぞ。", "name": "疑念を捨てた島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_021"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "車がない……？", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ここに来るまでに気が付かなかったのか？　この島に車なんてないんだ。", "name": "同じく疑念を捨てた島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "でも、道路は整備されて……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_021", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "むかし観光客を呼び込もうとして道路を作ったんだが、完成しても誰も来なかったのさ。結局、金がかかっただけで赤字になっちまった。", "name": "疑念を捨てた島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_021"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嬢ちゃん、急いでるならこの自転車を貸そうか？", "name": "疑念を捨てた島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_021"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "古いやつだが、まだ何とか使える。頑張って漕げば、別荘まで二時間くらいで着けるはずだ。", "name": "疑念を捨てた島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_021"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子は男の背後にある古びた自転車に目を向けた。フレームは傷だらけで、塗装もほとんど剥がれ落ちている。見るからに年季の入った自転車という佇まいだ。"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "頑張れよ！　久しぶりに来たお客さんだからな、目当ての人が見つかるように祈ってるよ。それと、島を楽しんでいってくれ！", "name": "同じく疑念を捨てた島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1002_1#1$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ありがとうございます。それでは、わたくしはここで。", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子がペダルを軽く踏むと――"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_bicyclegallop", "volume": 0.8, "loop": "true", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "豊川祥子", "content": "なんとか、走れそう……"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "豊川祥子", "content": "ですわね！"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_021", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "気をつけろ！　前は下り坂――", "name": "疑念を捨てた島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_021"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "注意はもう手遅れだった。古びた自転車は制御不能になり、祥子は自転車ごと坂道を滑り落ちていった。"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_electrcwhlchrrll", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "きゃ――――！！！", "name": "豊川祥子"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_021", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "――ふふっ、面白いわね。", "name": "疑念を捨てた島民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_021"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_021", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_021", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_humanchange"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#19$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#19$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あっはははははは――", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#19$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ほんと――最高ね！　あははははは！", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#19$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1938_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "モ、モーフィアス。", "name": "ウォルフ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1938_1#2$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少し、やりすぎ、じゃ……", "name": "ウォルフ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1938_1#2$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黙りなさい。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1938_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "ウォルフ"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1938_1#2$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あいつが自分で勝負に乗ってきたんじゃない。私は勝負を進行しているだけ。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あいつの弱点、絶対に暴いてやるわ。そして二度と覚めない夢を紡ぐのよ。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "モーフィアス", "content": "思い知らせてあげる――"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "モーフィアス", "content": "私こそが、夢のお城最高の「夢の作り手」だってことをね。"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……アイリス。あんたが私より上なんてあり得ない。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g16_sunnyday_R1", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$saferoom_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太陽が真上に来て、木陰がどんどん狭まってきました……", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ちょっと暑くなってきちゃいましたね。", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "私の別荘がこの近くにあるんだ。そこでひと休みしない？", "name": "三角初華"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g6_noblelivingroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#1$2", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ふぅ――すっごく涼しいです！", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "リビングもとっても広いですね。ここまで広いと、冬場は寒くなっちゃいませんか？", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#8$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あそこの暖炉に火をつければ、すぐに暖かくなるんだ。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#1$2"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "でも私一人なら、ストーブをソファの傍に置くだけで十分だよ。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#1$2"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "うーん、初華さんがここまで立派なお嬢様だったなんて……", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#5$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#14$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "いやいや！　私はここに住んでいるんじゃなくて、この別荘を管理しているだけ。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#14$2"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小声）私、家主さんのお邪魔になっちゃいませんか……？", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#9$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#13$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大丈夫、今は私一人しか住んでないから。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#13$2"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ここの家主は……もう長い間帰ってないんだ。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "なんだか……その人が恋しいみたいですね。", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#1$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "うん。仕事の関係っていうより、私にとっては特別な関係だったから……", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あの子は、初めて私自身を見てくれた子っていうか……私と初めて親友になってくれた人でね。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あの子はピアノを弾くのが好きだった。私は傍で椅子に座って、ピアノに合わせて歌ってたんだ。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本当に……本当に楽しかったんだ。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "それなのに、どうしてその方は、この島を……この「家」を出てしまったんですか？", "name": "エイヤフィヤトラ"}, "figure_art": "avg_180_amgoat_1#11$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#12$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "どうしてだろうね……ここにずっといたいと思ってたのは、もしかしたら私のほうだけだったのかも。", "name": "三角初華"}, "figure_art": "avg_4184_dolris_1#9$2"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "41_g5_siestaunbuiltland_d", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_speedline", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_bicyclegallop", "loop": "true", "channel": "bse", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.8, "fadetime": 1.5, "channel": "bse"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自転車のきしむ音がますます激しくなり、祥子はバランスを取るだけで精一杯になっていた。"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そして、体力も徐々に限界へと近付いていた。"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_hastybell", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 25.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "きゃっ――！", "name": "豊川祥子"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "急カーブにさしかかった所で、自転車のブレーキが突然効かなくなり、祥子の身体は勢い余って投げ出された。"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bse", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 35.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.8, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothtrailground", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ううっ……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#2$2"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子は痛みをこらえながら身体を起こし、必死に顔を上げて目的地の方向を見据えた。"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遠くの山の麓に、一軒の家がかすかに見える。"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あれは……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "その家を見た祥子の脳裏には、何故か無数の知らない記憶が蘇ってきた――"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "こ、これは――！？", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初華はこの夢の中で、幼い頃から祥子とここで遊んでいた。"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そして成長してからは、ここで一緒に暮らすようになった。"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "これは……全部、初華の夢ですの……？", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstpwalk", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "o"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "o", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ふふん――♪　ふんふふん――♪", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ふふっ……どうかしら？　あの子には色んな夢を見せてあげたわ。だけど、結局あの子の願いは「あなたと一緒にいたい」ってだけなのよ。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#20$1"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そんな夢も、最後はいつもひとりぼっち。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "いつも、あんたが突然いなくなる――", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ほんと、あんたってつくづく酷い子ね。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 424, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そんな……酷いだなんて……", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 426, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あいつから聞いたんでしょ？", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夢に出てくるのは、心の奥底に眠るありのままの思いだって。三角初華が一緒にいたいと強く願えば願うほど、ますますあなたに手が届かなくなっていくわ。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ひと気のない小さな島を作ってあげても、そこを二人だけの島にしても……それでも、あの子は手に入れたものを失う辛さを何度も味わう運命なの。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結局あの子の幸せは、砂みたいに指の間からこぼれ落ちていっちゃうのよ。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "まったく、夢の中ですら救われないなんて、どれだけ絶望してるのかしらね。", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 432, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……初華、必ずあなたを悪夢から救い出しますわ。", "name": "豊川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#7$2"}, {"id": 434, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#19$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ほんと？　ほんとに！？", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#19$1"}, {"id": 436, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#21$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "楽しみにしてるわ――己の無力さに打ちのめされ、途方に暮れるあんたの顔をね！", "name": "モーフィアス"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#21$1"}, {"id": 438, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shipwhistle", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "モーフィアスが人目も憚らずに高笑いをする中、遠くから船の汽笛の音が響いてきた。"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "それは、出航の時間が迫っているという合図だった。"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}